<BlogPost
  title="How to use Claude Code for automated testing: unit, integration, and e2e"
  description="A practical guide to writing tests with Claude Code, setting up CLAUDE.md testing conventions, using subagents for parallel test runs, and working test-driven in practice."
  date="April 12, 2026"
